title: Which country singer has the most songs? - Quora

response.answer_text: Your question is not clear. Who has the most recordings? Who has written most songs? On the latter, I might guess Kris Kristofferson or Hank Williams, but there are probably songwriters that were not performers who had greater output.
Which country singer has the most songs? I'd have to say Dolly Parton who has written and recorded over 3000 songs. She is a country/pop music hit making machine in a five foot frame.
